<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.11">
<l>teyva nāyaka ṉāraṇaṉ ṟarivikkirama ṉaṭiyiṇaimicai</l>
<l>koykoḷ pūmpoḻil cūḻkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>ceyta vāyirat tuḷḷivai taṇcirī varamaṅkai</l>
<l>mēya pattuṭaṉ vaikal pāṭa vallār vāṉōrk kārā vamutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable to sing daily</l>
<l>these ten together associated with cool Cirīvaramaṅkai among the thousand made</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr surrounded by groves with flowers to be plucked</l>
<l>on the foot pair of Trivikrama, Nāraṇa, the leader of the gods</l>
	<l>[are] unending ambrosia to the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
